After disturbing photos of Nollywood actress, Regina Daniels surfaced online some days ago showing her loking lean, the actress has finally addressed the issue and that of her marriage to Ned Nwoko. In a new video posted on her Snapchat account, the 21-year-old told haters to back off as she loves her husband, Ned with all her heart. She said: “It’s not to my face… Can somebody please just help me tell my husband how much I love him so so so much. So fcck what y’all say but take it or not, I love you Mr Ned Nwoko, with all my heart” Watch video below: Source